      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDWEEK SCOTCHES (1) made light work of the tricky draw with a quick early sectional last time clocking 17.27 in a 5.5 lengths win at this track over 300m. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Looks the one to beat. GOLDEN SUNSET (3) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (17.72) in a NG at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Expected to feature again. TOMMIE'S BRIDE (8) should enjoy clear running from the outside box. Below best latest at this track (17.85) when 6th and beaten 5 lengths. Form here at this distance is strong including seven wins. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and three minor placings from seven starts. Can measure up this time. SHE'S SILKY (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
